snippet.description:

✅Project Gotham Racing: Mobile (J2ME) Walkthrough Gameplay

✅Project Gotham Racing: Mobile is an adaptation for mobile devices of the Xbox-exclusive Project Gotham Racing series. The game contains eight licensed cars and three cities (London, Paris and San Francisco) with three courses for each location. The available game modes are a solo career and a time trial mode. The solo career consists of several championships with multiple events. By completing them a next championship can be unlocked. There are regular street races against other cars, but also drifting challenges.

✅TITLE: Project Gotham Racing: Mobile
GENRE: Racing
PUBLISHER: Glu Mobile
RELEASE DATE: 2007
